data.description: Beautiful 20 acres just outside of Bridgeport, TX. This ranch is great for those who want to have a get-away recreational property. There are trophy class whitetail deer, turkey, pigs, and tons of other wildlife that come through this ranch. You can also come build your dream home with many sites that would be great for a house. From the front of the property you have great views looking west at the Texas sunsets. No gravel roads to get to this property. Give us a call today for a showing!
